GigaTux offers affording hosting in the UK, USA and Germany, always with a focus on Internet rights and anonymity. GigaTux accepts Bitcoins and has been a keen supporter of tor, offering a lot of bandwidth to the project. VPS hosting services are its speciality (with VPNs working just fine) but web site, domain name and dedicated server offerings are also available.

GigaTux opened in February 2007 and is keen to support hugely interesting technologies such as Bitcoin.

